<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sixteen Showcase</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@picocss/pico@2/css/pico.min.css">
  <style>
    main.container {
      max-width: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      padding-left: 1rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }
    article {
      max-width: 60rem;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    table {
      table-layout: auto;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .palette {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2px;
      flex-wrap: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .palette-swatch {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .theme-row {
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
    }
    .theme-row:hover {
      background-color: var(--pico-code-background-color);
      transform: scale(1.01);
    }
    .theme-row:active {
      transform: scale(0.99);
    }
    .variants {
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }
    .variant-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
      margin-right: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background-color: var(--pico-muted-border-color);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
    .variant-dark {
      background-color: #2c2c2c;
      color: #f0f0f0;
    }
    .variant-light {
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
      color: #2c2c2c;
    }
    .auto-indicator {
      color: var(--pico-muted-color);
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <h1>Sixteen Showcase</h1>
    <p>Many many themes</p>

    <article>
      <header>About Sixteen</header>
      <p>Sixteen is a Crystal library and CLI tool for working with Base-16 color themes following the Tinted Themes specification.</p>
      <p>Features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access 300+ Base-16 theme YAML files embedded in the binary</li>
        <li>Generate theme CSS with custom templates</li>
        <li>Auto-generate theme variants (dark â†” light)</li>
        <li>Browse themes interactively in the terminal</li>
        <li>Export themes in multiple formats</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/ralsina/sixteen">https://github.com/ralsina/sixteen</a>
      </p>
    </article>

    <table role="grid" class="striped">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Theme</th>
          <th>Palette</th>
          <th>Author</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#families}}
            {{{.}}}
        {{/families}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <footer>
      <hr>
      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/ralsina/sixteen">Sixteen</a> |
        <a href="https://github.com/ralsina/sixteen">GitHub</a> |
        <a href="https://sixteen.ralsina.me/">sixteen.ralsina.me</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
